name: SS Starfall
description:
Embark on a galactic adventure in space! Help a colony of cats find a new planet to call home.

Images generated with DALLE2 and/or Midjourney AIs. 

Royalty-free sound effects via pixabay.com

The game was inspired by my cat Juniper. This is an image of him as a baby in his cat carrier that looks like a spaceship! His DALLE2-extended image is in the second passage. 

You can follow his adventures here: https://www.instagram.com/handsomejuniperbarry/

Happy exploring!
